snippet.title: Diana Creates A Family Tree Through Photos
snippet.description:
Diana creates a Family Tree. She takes pictures of herself, mom, dad, Roma, and Oliver. The photos she takes are funny but not right for a school project! A fun family story about Diana's Family Tree.
